headline: Piper Sandler Highlights EQT’s (EQT) Infrastructure Plans and Near-Term Natural Gas Challenges
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) ranks among the best performing energy stocks to buy now. headline: Walt Disney, McDonald's, Palantir Set To Report Earnings
summary: Key earnings this week will include PLTR, ON, AMD, CAT, & PFE. With Trump's revised tariff orders, investors will be keeping an eye on economic reports releasing next week.
